492
00:38:42,570 --> 00:38:48,180
I must produce the show, and you must grab the customers.

493
00:38:50,050 --> 00:38:51,520
Yes...

494
00:38:55,850 --> 00:39:02,660
But, why would  Yum Yum Slurp Slurp  come to our Real Estate office?

